Note:
Curtis ( 1845 : 457 )
in describing this species stated: “several specimens from Valparaiso”. This is the only specimen of the type series of
P. laevicosta
available in BMNH . To fix the current interpretation of this name and to ensure stability, we are hereby designating this lectotype .
